snippet.title: Captain Beeble for the Atari 8-bit family
snippet.description:
Came also out for:

???


Game description:

You are Captain Beeble and have to collect a crystal to put it in the C.P.U. (Crystal Power Unit).

Shoot flying enemies for points and be aware of the huge rocks.


What I think:

Actually a good game, but it can be extremely frustrating and even somewhat unfair at times, as you bounce off of walls and if a rock is there you might crash into it.
